<p>To: Terrance D. Hell<br />
From: Georgio Decker<br />
Subject: RE: The Alpine Vista Killer, complete manuscript</p>
<p>Okay, so, reading the manuscript, I couldn’t help but notice that, after Gregory dropped and broke his power bank, he simply pulled out a second Einova 63W 20,000mAh Power Bank (again, oddly specific brand to put in literature). A bit of a letdown, if you ask me.</p>
<p>Best,<br />
Georgio Decker<br />
Senior Editor<br />
Death Bells Publishing</p>
